+	 * If the bpf-prog does not need the IP[46] header,  the
+	 * bpf-prog can avoid parsing the IP header by using
+	 * TCP_BPF_SYN.  Otherwise, the bpf-prog can get both
+	 * IP[46] and TCP header by using TCP_BPF_SYN_IP.
